description:
If you are interested in the project and feel like following us, you have earned an XP +2 badge that credits you to us as a curious art lurker in the Tangle. We hope you've found a gem. We work hard in the studio, the workshop and the mine to bring out precious, semi-precious and philosophical minerals.

We are in the absolute beginning. Follow us on 
Discord https://discord.gg/RPxXEtCQnz 
and Telegram https://t.me/+S9vKXiFhueozOTdk
Leave us a message so we can be clear about who you are and approve your badge

XP +2  60 % discount if you want to own one of our non-branded especial collector NFTs from TAG DODA series.
TAG DODA NFTs gives you "vidilla" in our society and future advantages and benefits for your artistic enjoyment.
